Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the truth is, this could be\Nmy true nature, for all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps Hirasaka-kun saw through that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course during that time, not for one\Nmoment did I forget about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the one who betrayed me, Ryuji Hirasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absurd that things have\Nturned out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop this foolishness\Nonce and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you give birth to a healthy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time I couldn't understand what\Nthe director was trying to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell us anything about that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well give her a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what, but can you\Ntalk to us about something more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pay attention to this Ren,\Nit doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It troubled me that he was always\Nexchanging e-mails with somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just got a little curious. That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Remi Shinjyo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Age: 27\NHeight: 160 cm\N3 Sizes: 87-59-86
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Blood Type: AB\NWeight: 47 kg\NDpt: Gynecology (Head nurse)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ako Fujisawa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Age: 23\NHeight: 157 cm\N3 Sizes: 88-60-90
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Blood Type: O\NWeight: 47 kg\NDpt: Provisional
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hikaru Kodama
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Age: 21\NHeight: 154 cm\N3 Sizes: 79-55-81
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Blood Type: B\NWeight: 43 kg\NDpt: General Care
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ren Nanase
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Age: 22\NHeight: 158 cm\N3 Sizes: 85-57-87
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Blood Type: AB\NWeight: 45 kg\NDpt: Gynecology
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sensei's tool...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... Sensei really loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This has to be some kind of sick joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I wanted to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I waited for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryuji Hirasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man who trifled with me, Ryuji Hirasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man who tried to rob the\Nlife of the child I carried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryuji Hirasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man I've hated more than\Nanyone else I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ryuji Hirasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My revenge and my ambition.\NMy future. My everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Hirasaka-kun.\NIf I allowed you to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}her child's life would be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That, above everything I wanted to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm the last one to feel that\Npain, then it's all ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Hirasaka-kun, I really did love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... you weren't serious about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I couldn't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye... Hirasaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hirasaka-Sensei was\Ntemporarily unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was able to miraculously\Nhold onto his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Jinguji was trying to\Nget even with him then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, we can't gain\Nanyone's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in regards to this case will\Nprobably disappear into the dark, I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it seems to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that the only part of your front\Nwhich is protruding at the\Nmoment is your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there still appears to be no\Nchange of color of your nipples.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Ren, do you feel it even\Nduring examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sensei you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is examination too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you become pregnant, this area\Nchanges color and odor too, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's this Ren, you\Nappear to be damp...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.34,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, if they get turned on when\Ngetting examined by the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's the patient that's the strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't say anything,\Nthen I won't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do down here exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, lie down on\Nyour side over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I'll take another\Nlook at your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our child is alive inside here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really believe it to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our baby, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei don't tell me you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it... Stop it please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it was our baby didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this charade! That's\NNaoya's damn kid, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cruel... aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take it out and\Nexamine it more thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fucking moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to listen to what I tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be you Sensei, but the one\Nthing I won't allow is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could a doctor, someone who\Nsaves lives, do this kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, this really is your baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you're the only one I've been with!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren, you've really become strong after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than just a woman, you've turned\Ninto a fully qualified mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.14,0:23:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just testing you is all. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as Sensei loves me, I don't\Neven mind being his tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... I just had to protect\Nthe baby inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.95,0:24:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I had to protect\Nmyself no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.48,0:24:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren... not you as well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.69,0:24:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to do this to me as well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the true form of the\Ncreature called "woman"...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.35,0:25:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.06,0:25:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I... really loved you, Ryuji Hirasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.23,0:25:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.32,0:25:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if her story was really the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.57,0:25:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.66,0:25:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was just an elaborate fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.25,0:25:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.08,0:25:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However when you're a detective\Nfor a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.96,0:25:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get to see this kind of case\Nevery once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.76,0:25:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And every time I do I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.97,0:25:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people's hearts are just darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.47,0:25:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a core that no one could desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.35,0:25:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're true darkness.
